          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-06-22T06:56:39.8682507Z",
          "locale_text": "“有音阵信号接入，但我无法识别来源。”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "esES",
      "text": "«Estamos recibiendo una señal de voco, pero no puedo identificar su origen».",
      "modification_date": "2026-06-22T06:56:24.2085860Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-06-22T06:56:24.2085862Z",
      "original_text": "\"We have an incoming vox-signal, but I cannot identify the source.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-06-22T06:56:24.2085877Z",
          "locale_text": "«Estamos recibiendo una señal de voco, pero no puedo identificar su origen»."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "jaJP",
      "text": "\"音声着信ですが、発信元がわかりません\"",
      "modification_date": "2026-04-15T13:58:38.7140960Z",
